The premiere of Hollywood movie ‘Coming to America 2’ was held yesterday, Friday March 5 in Lagos and some Nigerian celebrities appeared at the venue in grand style. It was a night of glitz and glam on the red carpet as various celebrities from Nollywood Actors, artists, Big Brother Naija stars, and comedians stormed the venue. Celebrities including reality star Nengi, Vee, Mercy Eke, actress Yvonne Jegede, Juliet Ibrahim among others were a few who were spotted at the event and they dazzled in their expensive outfits nicely designed by African fashion designers.